Hi Chris, Below please find our feedback on the Travel FAQ. Disclaimer at the base:
  • Can we link the PDS and TMD docs with universal links?
Please read the Product Disclosure Statement (PDS) and Target Market Determination (TMD) for further details. 'Claims' tab:
  • How do I make a claim?
Missing a space between #3 and the last paragraph
  • How can I get help while travelling?
Link the dial the hotline numbers. Also, the full stop after 24/7 - can we remove the underline? Wherever you are you can call our friendly specialist emergency assistance and claims team on +61 2 7202 0824 from overseas or 1300 633 811 within Australia 24/7. 'General' tab:
  • How can I reach the Stella team? / How can I get travel insurance? / What is Robin Assist? Link to dial the hotline numbers
  • What is travel insurance? / What does travel insurance not cover?
Link to PDS doc
  • Is my information kept confidential?
Link to Privacy Policy page 'Policy' tab:
  • Can I make changes or cancel my policy? / Can I extend my policy if I plan to travel longer?
Link to Stella Hub (once the link is available?)
  • Am I covered for trip cancellation? / Can I claim for lost or stolen baggage? / Am I covered if I take part in sports and activities during my trip? / Am I covered if travelling on a cruise? / What does the Snow Pack cover? / Am I covered for renting a vehicle? Link to PDS doc
  • What is Travel Assistance? / What is Emergency Assistance? Link to dial the hotline numbers
  • Can I claim for lost or stolen baggage? Remove underline "you select and is shown on your Certificate of Insurance:"
  • Am I covered for riding a motorbike or scooter overseas?
Change it to read 'if you hire a…' "…, you will be covered if your hire a motorcycle or moped…"
  • Do you cover pet boarding?
Missing a "to" in this sentence "… due to reasons beyond your control, we will cover up to AUD $50 per day to a maximum…"
  • Am I covered for renting a vehicle? The line spacing is strange in the 2nd sentence. Also missing the PDS doc link.
Thanks a lot, Vivian Vivian Yeung Brand & Campaign Marketing Manager Level 13, 50 Pitt St, Sydney NSW 2000 m 0470 416 709 e vivian@stellainsurance.com.au w http://stellainsurance.com.au/
